To compile and run this transformer, follow the steps below:
1) navigate to the part-1/scanner directory
2) run the command "make clean"
3) run the command "make"
4) navigate to the part-1/scanner/bin directory
5) run scanner (or scanner.exe on windows) on your input file
6) your output program will be placed in a a file with your input file's name
followed by .out in the part-1/scanner/bin directory